DTCN.PF_IngresoEstimado AS PF_IngresoEstimadoCN , DTCN.PF_RecAguayLuz AS PF_RecAguayLuzCN , DTCN.PF_ConfirmaCel AS PF_ConfirmaCelCN , DTCN.PF_ConfirmaMail AS PF_ConfirmaMailCN , DTCN.PF_VigenciaFMI AS PF_VigenciaFMICN, DTCN.PF_VigenciaConsData AS PF_VigenciaConsDataCN, dtcod1.NumeroDoc as NumeroDoccn, dtcod1.ApellidoPri as ApellidoPriCod1, dtcod1.ApellidoSdo as ApellidoSdoCod1, dtcod1.NombrePri as NombrePriCod1, dtcod1.NombreSdo as NombreSdoCod1, dtcod1.ActEconomica1 as ActEconomica1Cod1, dtcod1.ActEconomica2 as ActEconomica2Cod1, DTCOD1.TerceroID as TerceroIDcod1, DTCOD1.FechaExpDoc as FechaExpDoccod1, dtcod1.PF_FincaRaiz AS PF_FincaRaizCod1, dtcod1.PF_MorasActuales AS PF_MorasActualesCod1, dtcod1.PF_MorasUltAno AS PF_MorasUltAnoCod1, dtcod1.PF_RepNegativos AS PF_RepNegativosCod1, dtcod1.PF_EstadoActual AS PF_EstadoActualCod1, dtcod1.PF_Probabilidad AS PF_ProbabilidadCod1, dtcod1.PF_Estabilidad AS PF_EstabilidadCod1, dtcod1.PF_Ubicabilidad AS PF_UbicabilidadCod1, dtcod1.PF_PorMaxFinancia AS PF_PorMaxFinanciaCod1, dtcod1.IngresosSOP AS IngresosSOPCod1, dtcod1.PF_IngresoEstimado AS PF_IngresoEstimadoCod1, dtcod1.PF_RecAguayLuz AS PF_RecAguayLuzCod1, dtcod1.PF_ConfirmaCel AS PF_ConfirmaCelCod1, dtcod1.PF_ConfirmaMail AS PF_ConfirmaMailCod1, dtcod1.PF_VigenciaFMI AS PF_VigenciaFMICod1, dtcod1.PF_VigenciaConsData AS PF_VigenciaConsDataCod1, dtcod2.ApellidoPri as ApellidoPriCod2, dtcod2.ApellidoSdo as ApellidoSdoCod2, dtcod2.NombrePri as NombrePriCod2, dtcod2.NombreSdo as NombreSdoCod2, dtcod2.ActEconomica1 as ActEconomica1Cod2, dtcod2.ActEconomica2 as ActEconomica2Cod2, dtcod2.NumeroDoc as NumeroDocCod2, DTcod2.TerceroID as TerceroIDcod2, DTcod2.FechaExpDoc as FechaExpDoccod2, dtcod2.PF_FincaRaiz AS PF_FincaRaizcod2, dtcod2.PF_MorasActuales AS PF_MorasActualescod2, dtcod2.PF_MorasUltAno AS PF_MorasUltAnocod2, dtcod2.PF_RepNegativos AS PF_RepNegativoscod2, dtcod2.PF_EstadoActual AS PF_EstadoActualcod2, dtcod2.PF_Probabilidad AS PF_Probabilidadcod2, dtcod2.PF_Estabilidad AS PF_Estabilidadcod2, dtcod2.PF_Ubicabilidad AS PF_Ubicabilidadcod2, dtcod2.PF_PorMaxFinancia AS PF_PorMaxFinanciacod2, dtcod2.IngresosSOP AS IngresosSOPcod2, dtcod2.PF_IngresoEstimado AS PF_IngresoEstimadocod2, dtcod2.PF_RecAguayLuz AS PF_RecAguayLuzcod2, dtcod2.PF_ConfirmaCel AS PF_ConfirmaCelcod2, dtcod2.PF_ConfirmaMail AS PF_ConfirmaMailcod2, dtcod2.PF_VigenciaFMI AS PF_VigenciaFMIcod2, dtcod2.PF_VigenciaConsData AS PF_VigenciaConsDatacod2, DO.Alternativa1, DO.Alternativa2, DO.Alternativa3, DO.Alternativa4, DO.Alternativa5, DO.Alternativa6, DO.Alternativa7, DO.FactorAlt1, DO.FactorAlt2, DO.FactorAlt3, DO.FactorAlt4, DO.FactorAlt5, DO.FactorAlt6, DO.FactorAlt7, DO.MontoAlt1, DO.MontoAlt2, DO.MontoAlt3, DO.MontoAlt4, DO.MontoAlt5, DO.MontoAlt6, DO.MontoAlt7, DO.GarantiaAlt1, DO.GarantiaAlt2, DO.GarantiaAlt3, DO.GarantiaAlt4, DO.GarantiaAlt5, DO.GarantiaAlt6, DO.GarantiaAlt7, DT.PF_IngresosMin1, DT.PF_IngresosMin2, DT.PF_IngresosMin3, DT.PF_IngresosMin4, DT.PF_IngresosMin5, DT.PF_IngresosMin6, DT.PF_IngresosMin7, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin1 as PF_IngresosMin1CN, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin2 as PF_IngresosMin2CN, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin3 as PF_IngresosMin3CN, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin4 as PF_IngresosMin4CN, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin5 as PF_IngresosMin5CN, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin6 as PF_IngresosMin6CN, DTcn.PF_IngresosMin7 as PF_IngresosMin7CN, DT.PF_NumHipotecas, DT.PF_NumBienes, DT.PF_Restricciones, DT.PF_AntCompra, DT.PF_UltAnotacion, DTCN.PF_NumHipotecas as PF_NumHipotecasCN, DTCN.PF_NumBienes as PF_NumBienesCN, DTCN.PF_Restricciones as PF_RestriccionesCN, DTCN.PF_AntCompra as PF_AntCompraCN, DTCN.PF_UltAnotacion as PF_UltAnotacionCN, DTCOD1.PF_NumHipotecas AS PF_NumHipotecasCod1, DTCOD1.PF_NumBienes AS PF_NumBienesCod1, DTCOD1.PF_Restricciones AS PF_RestriccionesCod1, DTCOD1.PF_AntCompra as PF_AntCompraCod1, DTCOD1.PF_UltAnotacion as PF_UltAnotacionCod1 , DTCOD2.PF_NumHipotecas as PF_NumHipotecasCod2, DTCOD2.PF_NumBienes as PF_NumBienesCod2, DTCOD2.PF_Restricciones as PF_RestriccionesCod2, DTCOD2.PF_AntCompra as PF_AntCompraCod2, DTCOD2.PF_UltAnotacion as PF_UltAnotacionCod2, DV.Marca, DV.Referencia, DV.Modelo, DV.Carroceria, (case when Dv.Servicio = 1 then 'Particular' when Dv.Servicio = 2 then 'Publico' end) as servicio, DV.CeroKmInd, DV.Chasis, DV.PrecioVenta, dv.FasecoldaCod, DV.VlrFasecolda, Sol.VlrSolicitado, cast(Sol.VlrSolicitado / DO.VlrGtiaEvaluacion as decimal )as PorcSolicitado, DO.MontoMaximo, DO.CubriendoInd, ase.Descriptivo, DO.EstimadoSeguros, Sol.VlrPoliza, DO.VlrMensualSV, cast(Sol.VlrFinanciaSeguro - Sol.VlrPoliza as decimal) as OtrasFinanciacion, DO.MaxFinanciacionAut, DO.Plazo, DO.EstimadoObl, DO.CuotaFin, DO.CuotaSeg, DO.CuotaTotal, CU.DireccionDir1, CU.DireccionDir2, CU.DireccionDir3, CU.DireccionOtra, CUC.DireccionDir1 as DireccionDir1CN, CUC.DireccionDir2 as DireccionDir2CN, CUC.DireccionDir3 as DireccionDir3CN, CUC.DireccionOtra as DireccionOtraCN, --DT.PF_RecAguayLuz as PF_RecAguayLuzCN, --DT.PF_VigenciaConsData as PF_VigenciaConsDataCN, --DTCN.PF_RecAguayLuz as PF_RecAguayLuzCN, --DTCN.PF_VigenciaConsData as PF_VigenciaConsDataCN, --DTCOD1.PF_RecAguayLuz as PF_RecAguayLuzCOD1, --DTCOD1.PF_VigenciaConsData as PF_VigenciaConsDataCod1, --DTCOD2.PF_RecAguayLuz as PF_RecAguayLuzCod2, --DTCOD2.PF_VigenciaConsData as PF_VigenciaConsDataCod2, DO.Estado, DO.Calificacion, DO.Revision, DO.CargoResp, DO.Firma1Ind, DO.Firma2Ind, usuresp.Descriptivo as UsuarioResp, usu1.Descriptivo as UsuarioFirma1, usu2.Descriptivo as UsuarioFirma2, DO.FechaFirmaResp, DO.FechaFirma1, DO.FechaFirma2 FROM ccSolicitudDocu SOL with(nolock) INNER JOIN ccCliente CLI with(nolock) ON SOL.ClienteRadica = CLI.ClienteID AND SOL.eg_ccCliente= CLI.EmpresaGrupoID INNER JOIN coTercero TER with(nolock) ON SOL.ClienteRadica = TER.TerceroID AND CLI.eg_coTercero = TER.EmpresaGrupoID LEFT JOIN coTercero Cod1 with(nolock) ON SOL.Codeudor1 = Cod1.TerceroID LEFT JOIN glDocumentoControl CTL with(nolock) ON SOL.NumeroDoc = CTL.NumeroDoc LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosPersonales dt with(nolock) ON SOL.NumeroDoc = dt.NumeroDoc and dt.TipoPersona=1 and sol.VersionNro = dt.version LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosPersonales dtcn with(nolock) ON SOL.NumeroDoc = dtcn.NumeroDoc and dtcn.TipoPersona=2 and sol.VersionNro = dtcn.version LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosPersonales dtcod1 with(nolock) ON SOL.NumeroDoc = dtcod1.NumeroDoc and dtcod1.TipoPersona=3 and sol.VersionNro = dtcod1.version LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosPersonales dtcod2 with(nolock) ON SOL.NumeroDoc = dtcod2.NumeroDoc and dtcod2.TipoPersona=4 and sol.VersionNro = dtcod2.version LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosPersonales dtcod3 with(nolock) ON SOL.NumeroDoc = dtcod3.NumeroDoc and dtcod3.TipoPersona=5 and sol.VersionNro = dtcod3.version LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosOtros do ON SOL.NumeroDoc = do.NumeroDoc and sol.VersionNro = do.Version LEFT JOIN drSolicitudDatosVehiculo DV ON SOL.NumeroDoc = dV.NumeroDoc and sol.VersionNro = dV.Version LEFT JOIN ccAseguradora Ase ON do.AseguradoraID= Ase.AseguradoraID and sol.VersionNro = dV.Version LEFT JOIN ccSolicitudDataCreditoUbica CU ON SOL.NumeroDoc = CU.NumeroDoc and sol.VersionNro = CU.Version AND CU.NumeroId=DT.TerceroID and sol.VersionNro = cu.Version LEFT JOIN ccSolicitudDataCreditoUbica CUC ON SOL.NumeroDoc = CU.NumeroDoc and sol.VersionNro = CU.Version AND CUC.NumeroId=DTCN.TerceroID and sol.VersionNro = cuc.Version LEFT JOIN seUsuario usuresp ON do.UsuarioResp = usuresp.UsuarioID LEFT JOIN seUsuario usu1 ON do.UsuarioResp = usu1.UsuarioID LEFT JOIN seUsuario usu2 ON do.UsuarioResp = usu2.UsuarioID where ctl.EmpresaID=@empresaid and sol.Libranza=@Libranza order by ctl.FechaDoc desc
